{
  "stem": "14613.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I remember one day-- and really, the proper word is they smuggled my father from ghetto, not in a car, in a horse and buggy.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were not too many cars there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they took my father out of the ghetto to a-- to a German businessman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I think it was the name Scheibler and Grohman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And these are the people that my father did business-- they used to dye some of the textiles for my father.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I know that my father, in the beginning of the war, send a lot of materials to him for keeping, for safe-- for safekeeping.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And since we were thrown in ghetto, they took him out from the ghetto, brought him to this-- to the other friend of our father, so that my father could settle with him some accounts.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I know that he paid him for the materials.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that even in ghetto, replying to your question, we were still relatively sheltered at the beginning, because my father had more money.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in ghetto, for money you could buy extra food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that at the beginning, it was-- we were much better off than by and large the population.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father also had a certain conviction that he did not want to take any-- any role in-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He did not want to be a resort director, or anything like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because his thinking was-- and he said, that if I were to take a leadership position in these times.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And have much more for myself, I could not look other people straight in the eyes after the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he did not take any leadership position.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
